thumb.title: DANCE DELIGHTFUL COVER - SETE UTAU RELEASE
thumb.description: Alright, I finally decided to build up the courage to finally release Sete Utau. Love this song but can't replicate its MV due to my epilepsy. But I made custom art for it! I hope you all enjoy. You can also find Sete's Japanese VCV bank for download on the Utau Wiki! I hope you all enjoy him we much as I do.
